params.stealthRecipient: The address of the recipient of the transfer.

generateStealthAddress(uint256,address).details: Generates Stealth Address on behalve of a registered user.  The caller executes this function locally to compute a stealth address  that can be accessed by recipient.  Further, function computes a Public Key of the secret that can be published.

params._PubKeyX: The X public key coordinate of the registrant.
params._PubKeyY: The Y public key coordinate of the registrant.

params._registrant: The address whose keys to lookup.

returns.PubKeyX: X public key coordinate of public key
returns.PubKeyY: Y public key coordinate of public key

emitAnnoucement(address,bytes).notice: Emits event with information on the stealth-address transfer.

generateStealthAddress(uint256,address).notice: The public key of the owner must be stored within the contract.

registerKey(address,uint256,uint256).notice: Returns the stealth key associated with an address.

stealthKeys(address).notice: Returns the stealth key associated with an address.
